_sText:
improved version of version 1 of this map, i added a basement (and yes its supposed to be dark down their)
 also added another part with a house and whatever :D. also their is a few teleport's to hidden / high up places. 

(i got rid off most of the floating objects and the silly stack of containers)

if anything needs improving please tell me.

also their is an invisible ladder on one of the corners of the big water tank if your wondering how to get in it, then once your inside it their is a hidden room under the big water tank, find your way inside and you may just find out you will be safe, also under their is a teleport.

quite a few hidden areas in the map.... find them
